transformers_text: Sai ky Jump Japanese Hepburn Sai ky Jan pu is a Japanese monthly sh nen manga magazine published by Shueisha The magazine was started on December 3 2010 with three completely original titles and seven spin off manga from series in Weekly Sh nen Jump and V Jump 2 Originally a quarterly magazine Sai ky Jump became a monthly publication in December 2011 3 before switching to publishing once every 2 months with the November 2014 issue 4 It switched back to a monthly schedule with the September 2021 issue 5 The magazine's mascot was created by Eiichiro Oda 6 Shueisha estimated that the vast majority of Sai ky Jump readers are elementary school aged children 58 5 being upper elementary school aged and 28 being lower elementary school aged 1
